Package ca.odell.glazedlists.io

Interface Summary
ByteCoder An utility interface for converting Objects to bytes for storage or network transport.
NetworkListStatusListener Listens to the current status of a NetworkList.
 

Class Summary
CachingList An EventList that caches elements from its source EventList.
FileList An EventList that is persisted to disk.
GlazedListsIO A factory for creating all sorts of objects to be used with Glazed Lists.
ListPeer A ListPeer manages the network resources for publishing and subscribing to NetworkLists.
NetworkList<E> An EventList that is either published to the network or subscribed from the network.
